Package: inrep
Type: Package
Title: Instant Reports for Adaptive Assessments
Version: 0.3.0
Date: 2025-12-06
Author: Clievins Selva [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9980-7127>)
Authors@R: person(given = "Clievins", family = "Selva", email = "selva@uni-hildesheim.de", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9980-7127"))
Maintainer: Clievins Selva <selva@uni-hildesheim.de>
Description: A framework for administering assessments with web-based interfaces via 'Shiny'.
    Supports fixed and adaptive testing workflows, item bank validation, item selection,
    reporting utilities, and optional parallel processing helpers. Intended for
    psychological, educational, and survey research use cases.
URL: https://github.com/selvastics/inrep
BugReports: https://github.com/selvastics/inrep/issues
